|cat=Plugins/Validation/Validator
|return=Integer
|desc=Returns the number of invalid fields.
|longdesc=This depends on the internal validator state. It covers all fields only after validating the complete form (on submit or via $("form").valid()). After validating a single element, only that element is counted. Most useful in combination with the invalidHandler-option.
